{"tid":367073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［唔講唔知］原來湯渣，袁国强，馬道立，石永泰係同一個chamber出身","createTime":"2017-08-20T13:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T15:52:02.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5971ff877b129f0c14ecdb7cd6590c4a21ebd42","tid":367073,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/211240_a04e088156353afc3e26437e33d1f996.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F211240_a04e088156353afc3e26437e33d1f996.jpg&h=5e90832f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/211242_edbea2609e12a62c1920b5615284a1e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F211242_edbea2609e12a62c1920b5615284a1e5.jpg&h=9db4c16b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/15638/石永泰-發表意見前唔該declare一下自己係乜chamber先\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F15638%2F%E7%9F%B3%E6%B0%B8%E6%B3%B0-%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E6%84%8F%E8%A6%8B%E5%89%8D%E5%94%94%E8%A9%B2declare%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E4%BF%82%E4%B9%9Cchamber%E5%85%88&d=kpl4clYGq9c0wyuU2hhfGrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a24dc8bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/15638/石永泰-發表意見前唔該declare一下自己係乜chamber先</a>"},{"pid":"7ed534ca45fb6865cb9bcd454e2092dc7aeecb86","tid":367073,"uid":61280,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:16:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同Chamber又點？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實世柒今次真係柒出宇宙，自暴其短，少見多怪！！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"690e7a95436e5b688e3213e1dc8e88dc30f25011","tid":367073,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"黃世柒篇文：<br />\n<br />\n照平日 石永泰 講嘢嘅作風，照計唔會講呢啲湯家驊級數嘅言論㗎。只不過，大家一check石永泰個Chamber個list，我心諗， 石永泰 唔該declare the interest或者 rescue himself ，都唔好攞自己間Chamber嚟玩，一被公眾知道係好鬼核突<br />\n<br />\n無錯， 石永泰 係 Temple Chamber嘅Head of Chamber，而湯家驊同一間Chamber，呢件事都未最爆機，更爆機喺個history部門<br />\n <br />\n無錯，呢間 Chamber 出過三位律政司同律政司司長，包括咗英治時代嘅唐明治，中國管治年代嘅黃仁龍，仲有大家都近排憎到佢入骨嘅袁國強。我唔係法律界人士，我都知表面上，大狀係獨行俠嚟，Chamber叫大家夾份用啲resource，但如果大家用得同一個Chamber，呢班友啲關係都唔係點個頭say hi果啲「同事」喇，仲要連埋 石永泰 在內，成村人都做得大律師公會嘅主席， 石永泰 你話自己唔識湯家驊同袁國強都無人信喇。好彩楊振權生涯做大狀嘅時間唔長，搵唔番佢邊間Chamber，同埋同一個Chamber，都有一個敢言嘅法官王式英，否則你 石永泰 呢劑幫朋友，真係幫到自己個朵都臭鬼晒。<br />\n<br />\n其實由今日灣仔嘅遊行人數嚟睇，公眾嘅判斷好清楚，唔好同我講戴耀廷求仁得仁呢啲嘢，依家香港公眾要求嘅法院係公正行事，唔可以the instrument of terror。德國聯邦人權專員嘅聲明，其實正係紐倫堡法官大審邏輯嘅演繹嚟，縱使國會大廈縱火案捉咗個保加利亞人，法院當時都判無罪釋放，之後希特拉至發狂搞「人民法院」出嚟。依家香港部分司法界人士，應該係時候睇番德國嘅歷史，唔捍衛法治嘅結果，一係保唔住自己條命，一係臭名永留。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但認真嗰chamber由最正常到最仆街都有<br />\n世柒用同一個chamber屌人唔多valid"},{"pid":"fd642f446c9ce8c64a1454a61969e801e784cf3a","tid":367073,"uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同Chamber又點？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實世柒今次真係柒出宇宙，自暴其短，少見多怪！！！</span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺冇大關係<br />\n但見識少唔知原來哩個chamber咁撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b49f7c75aba6eb68fb605e18c30838cc7bc890","tid":367073,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:20:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同Chamber又點？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<